{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Go forth, it is you who will save the universes... from annihilation.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/game_info.png?t=1731448532\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cappi: Starbound Saga is a 2D platformer with gameplay styles inspired by the Kirby and Sonic series. With Cappi, use powerful abilities and maintain speed to be able to save the galaxy in record time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0\u00a0 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/the_cast.png?t=1731448532\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/lives_cappi.png?t=1731448532\" />Cappi Starr is a young star traveler who wishes to speed through the galaxy carefree someday.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/lives_atlas.png?t=1731448532\" />Atlas Zan is an intergalactic geologist traveling with Cappi to learn more of the worlds and remind Cappi of his duty as a Hero of Light.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/lives_ruv.png?t=1731448532\" />Ruv Hector Drevalin is a wandering swordsman hanging with Cappi to uphold his motto of keeping justice in the galaxy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/mechanics.png?t=1731448532\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cappi is very versatile and diverse in his kit and abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/ezgif-4-191a447c23.gif?t=1731448532\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cappi is equipped at all times with his trusty <strong>Prism</strong> <strong>Yoyo</strong>. He can swing it <strong>horizontally and vertically</strong> to catch foes high and low. Cappi also can stomp on the ground to attack foes relentlessly or to catch his bearings. It can also be used to go down slopes to gain great speed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/ezgif-4-3dcd54cd80.gif?t=1731448532\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In addition to this, Cappi and use the abilities of defeated enemies to power up his yoyo!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/ezgif-4-d19b128069.gif?t=1731448532\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Using these abilities, his damage, moveset and mobility get an upgrade or are completely new! Use the abilities to your advantage to mow down the Cursed and make it to the goal quickly and easily!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Time Thief","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3232760/657623265a2f557f041b512645a148dda182aec0.jpg"},{"name":"Dream Defender","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3232760/ea1146ea035e18236f82f40f6c0bc015ea9a687b.jpg"},{"name":"Dream Warrior","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3232760/c3a5039eef83e4bfc488cd1178b2a4d276308020.jpg"},{"name":"Parry Patrol","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3232760/2bdd9610f115ec62903cfb36acedaf8724682e22.jpg"},{"name":"Aquaphobia","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3232760/bdd54db3e03e20a0bf7c84dc244413bb6665744a.jpg"},{"name":"Novice Spelunker","path":"https://cdn.akama