ngs. It can also be used to go down slopes to gain great speed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/ezgif-4-3dcd54cd80.gif?t=1731448532\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In addition to this, Cappi and use the abilities of defeated enemies to power up his yoyo!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/extras/ezgif-4-d19b128069.gif?t=1731448532\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Using these abilities, his damage, moveset and mobility get an upgrade or are completely new! Use the abilities to your advantage to mow down the Cursed and make it to the goal quickly and easily!</p>","developers":["Snowski"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232760/header.jpg?t=1731448532","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257066751,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257066751/movie480.mp4?t=1729357178","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257066751/movie_max.mp4?t=1729357178"},"name":"STEAM TRAILER","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257066751/26c48475a9cfca97a0a0975e537617a6f8066464/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1729357178","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257066751/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1729357178","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257066751/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1729357178"}}],"name":"Cappi: Starbound Saga","package_groups":[{"description":"","display_type":0,"is_recurring_subscription":"false","name":"default","save_text":"","selection_text":"Select a purchase option","subs":[{"can_get_free_licen